    "body" : "<p>I use the blow function in my GeneralUtils class, check it may be useful</p>\n\n<pre><code>    public String getFieldType(Object o) {\n    if (o == null) {\n        return \"Unable to identify the class name\";\n    }\n    return o.getClass().getName();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
